{"tid":356330,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"(弱智系列）台妹拍片俾章魚吸自己對奶出意外！導致蜂窩性組織炎緊急住院","createTime":"2017-08-12T03:57:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-13T07:50:00.000Z","uid":12709,"like":4,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0a3106057bc32f5f0deb85fe884a9f8c5ce04f82","tid":356330,"uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T03:57:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://star.ettoday.net/news/987294?from=fb_et_pets\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstar.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F987294%3Ffrom%3Dfb_et_pets&d=OqD2C0xP3Ur7qn00Z6%2FwtdU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=e2d65b48\" target=\"_blank\">http://star.ettoday.net/news/987294?from=fb_et_pets</a><br />\n2017年08月11日 23:03<br />\n<br />\n記者劉宜庭／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n網路紅人宛宛兒在鏡頭前，總是給人瘋癲、搞笑，以及不拘小節的開朗形象，深受許多粉絲喜愛。不過，她11日突然發文透露，自己因為被章魚咬到，導致罹患蜂窩性組織炎而住院，打針過程更是崩潰大哭，引來不少網友關心、直呼心疼！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2723/e2723373.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2723%2Fe2723373.jpg&h=33c9506b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲宛宛兒被章魚咬傷，因蜂窩性組織炎住院。（圖／翻攝自宛宛兒臉書）<br />\n<br />\n宛宛兒11日下午在臉書上發文透露，自己人在和平醫院急診室，因為遭章魚咬傷的關係，罹患蜂窩性組織炎，還因此導致必須住院，並PO出吊點滴、手指包紮的照片，畫面令大票粉絲心疼不已。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2723/d2723374.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2723%2Fd2723374.jpg&h=80f7829a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲▼宛宛兒挨4針飆淚。（圖／翻攝自宛宛兒臉書）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2723/d2723372.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2723%2Fd2723372.jpg&h=46988b1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過，宛宛兒在打針的過程中，因為護士找不到血管，一連挨了4針，為此忍不住淚崩，「好痛啊！我太肥看不到血管。」接著，她也被護士問及受傷原因，「我說被章魚咬，她滿頭黑人問號我們倆個都笑了，太智障了。」<br />\n<br />\n原來，宛宛兒10日錄影前，先是PO出一段章魚的影片預告，「<span style=\"color: red;\">我等一下要拍一個東西，就是要被這隻章魚吸，我要被這隻章魚、我要抓著牠然後被牠吸住我的奶欸。</span>」她為此感到十分緊張，但為了工作只好拼了，沒想到卻意外因此而受傷，在錄影的過程中遭章魚咬傷，才緊急就醫並得知需住院的消息，「第一次工作中大哭，原來章魚會咬人，而且咬完會整隻手腫又刺又麻，臭章魚。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2723/d2723369.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2723%2Fd2723369.jpg&h=0c898308&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲宛宛兒原本錄影預計要任章魚吸奶。（圖／翻攝自宛宛兒臉書）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2723/d2723368.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2723%2Fd2723368.jpg&h=c0238396&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲宛宛兒遭章魚咬傷大哭，緊急就醫打破傷風。（圖／翻攝自宛宛兒臉書）<br />\n<br />\n在宛宛兒住院消息曝光後，隨即也引來大票網友留言關心，「還好宛爺有馬上就醫，相信很快就會好的」、「太扯了啦」、「早日康復，快點回到可愛又活潑的宛宛兒」、「太嚴重了啦，宛爺多休息，保重身體喔」，希望她能夠早日康復。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2723/d2723371.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2723%2Fd2723371.jpg&h=c8178cfe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲宛宛兒手指被章魚咬傷。（圖／翻攝自宛宛兒臉書）<br />\n<br />\n▼宛宛兒原本錄影預計要任章魚吸奶。（影片／取自宛宛兒臉書，如遭刪除請見諒。）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/Momoyo520/videos/874814139361050/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2FMomoyo520%2Fvideos%2F874814139361050%2F&d=OqD2C0xP3Ur7qn00Z6%2FwtdU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=f7ffa580\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/Momoyo520/videos/874814139361050/</a><br />\n<br />\n到底有幾弱智先做得出呢啲野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce66405c499b0558626ba89420e018ac5becd139","tid":356330,"uid":82532,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T03:59:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://s2.quickmeme.com/img/2f/2f01ffc109d37740e94cd5d685f1a18460f2da1b56510d021667d89dc76e1379.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs2.quickmeme.com%2Fimg%2F2f%2F2f01ffc109d37740e94cd5d685f1a18460f2da1b56510d021667d89dc76e1379.jpg&h=370fce43&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1f4e683b2b647201092601d116c1a8558e4f55dc","tid":356330,"uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T04:26:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d5b04951306f74d72a7c2f4336efb3686f22929","tid":356330,"uid":116759,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T04:28:23.000Z","msg":"冇腦都算 仲要冇樣冇身材<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8da3fe2cb9707f5407ff468a4da8d01681d76cf0","tid":356330,"uid":73318,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T04:34:15.000Z","msg":"好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">隻章魚</span>"},{"pid":"b59fdca7cac48dd4b7939fa2380c07ce13769075","tid":356330,"uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T04:37:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9476d65c42e3a02c609e654256859c36aa2d8ca","tid":356330,"uid":60169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T05:01:48.000Z","msg":"柒到盡頭便是型"},{"pid":"c99135c60c6c088ee30dbc6a0658c5bf8f4771bb","tid":356330,"uid":46435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T05:04:35.000Z","msg":"真係豬西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30bc62f51c279db3110d95c6c3727436cd4b73d5","tid":356330,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T05:07:52.000Z","msg":"扮美人魚咩"},{"pid":"6519d777b97de9606eded920e438a314036adc47","tid":356330,"uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T06:21:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2697edb4a53cb684f7e7d9a039316c73b90a0bf7","tid":356330,"uid":62856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T06:26:47.000Z","msg":"俾章魚咬會有咩超能力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif